title: September 30, 2015 - Guelph Fire Prevention Day is October 10 (City of Guelph)
text: ( Source : City of Guelph ) Guelph, ON , September 30 , 2015 - The Guelph Fire Department is hosting its annual Fire Prevention Day on Saturday, October 10 . The event is open to the public and runs from 10 a.m. to 2 p.m. at the Guelph Costco,
